<div id="Idea_2883"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2883-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2883">mechanism to retract vote and prioritize vote&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">polarbear4</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">9 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">A button to retract a vote in this Dialogue would be helpful.  I accidentally clicked on the wrong one.  Also, one might want to retract votes from those that are not as important to one at the moment. <br/><br/>In addtion, a 1-4 rating might be helpful.  For instance, single-payer health care and campaign finance reform might be priority one, while transparency initiatives, while important, could be more lengthy projects.</div>
